0.040   2019-06-23 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add options: --start-at (-s), --start-stopped (-S).

	- Tweak Getopt::Long configuration.


0.03    2016-07-30 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add option to show banner ASCII art of mm:ss instead
	  (--banner-size).


0.02    2014-09-11 (PERLANCAR)

        - Add Enter as alias for S (start/stop).

        - Change default refresh rate from 0.01s to 0.02s.

        - Add whitespace at the end so cursor is less distracting.


0.01    2014-09-09 (PERLANCAR)

        - First release.
